commit.message: Fix the actions' RPC version bitfield
Allow sorting torrents by time to finish

Add last activity time as a sort option

Per https://github.com/tremc/tremc/issues/100.

Safely display filter and sort order in status line

They may be wider than the terminal, resulting in an exception, so slice the printed string accordingly.
Can avoid displaying the last character, since it will be overwritten by the up/down rates anyway.
Don't show total percent done if it is 100

Use ratio of upload to seed limit for paused complete torrents

For complete torrents which have a seed ratio limit, the progress bar
shows progress towards the seed ratio limit. Use the same progress
also for paused complete torrents.

This is related to https://github.com/tremc/tremc/issues/63

commit.message: Don't crash on torrent in another status

Fix bug that causes wanted size not showing correctly

'wanted' field for files from server has values 0/1, not False/True.

Catch any exception in get_reponse()

If the reuest takes too long (e.g. move large torrent on slow HDD), an exception is raised by request.read().

Reset visual mode when leaving torrent details view

Also, always leave details view by calling self.action_leave_details(), instead of setting the necessary attributes directly.

Return default attributes for non existent element name

Better than raising an exception (and crashing)?
See bc2d65f4f for an example of such bug.

Fix crash when more than 9999 files are listed

File index has 4 places, so the line is pushed further for index 10000 or more, so the file priority position is moved.
If file has zero size, don't draw pieces map

Add error mode as a filter option

Per https://github.com/tremc/tremc/issues/108

Transmission has 3 separate error modes: tracker warning, tracker error, local error.
Currently all are filtered together, as I expect errors to be rare. Is there a reason
to consider each mode separately?

Some filter dialog fixes for filters with a selection submenu

* sort list of options
* use also numbers for selection keys
* avoid crash when there are more options than selection keys
Allow for filtering trackerless torrents, by setting tracker to string "None".

Add action for adding filter in disjunction to current filter list

add_filter_line adds a filter in a new line. Thus, the new filtered i OR'ed with the other filters.
Default shortcut: ^T.
Change names of invert_filters and invert_filters_action
Add a new torrent list filter: torrents which are only partly wanted
